<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Statute lims:pit-date="2003-04-03" lims:lastAmendedDate="2003-04-03" lims:current-date="2025-07-24" lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452836" lims:id="452836" bill-origin="commons" bill-type="govt-public" xml:lang="fr" in-force="yes" xmlns:lims="http://justice.gc.ca/lims"><Identification lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452837" lims:id="452837"><BillNumber>C-227 </BillNumber><Parliament><Session>1</Session><Number>37</Number><RegnalYear><Year-s>49-50</Year-s><Monarch>Elizabeth II</Monarch></RegnalYear><Year-s>2001</Year-s></Parliament><LongTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452838" lims:id="452838">Loi instituant une journée nationale de commémoration de la bataille de la crête de Vimy</LongTitle><ShortTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452839" lims:id="452839" status="official">Loi sur le Jour de la bataille de Vimy</ShortTitle><RunningHead lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452840" lims:id="452840">Jour de la bataille de Vimy</RunningHead><BillHistory lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452841" lims:id="452841"><Stages lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" stage="consolidation"><Date><YYYY>2025</YYYY><MM>7</MM><DD>25</DD></Date></Stages><Stages lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452843" lims:id="452843" stage="assented-to"><Date><YYYY>2003</YYYY><MM>4</MM><DD>3</DD></Date></Stages></BillHistory><StatuteYear>2003</StatuteYear><Chapter lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452844" lims:id="452844"><ConsolidatedNumber official="no">V-1.8</ConsolidatedNumber><AnnualStatuteId revised-statute="no"><AnnualStatuteNumber>6</AnnualStatuteNumber><YYYY>2003</YYYY></AnnualStatuteId></Chapter></Identification><Introduction lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452845" lims:id="452845"><Preamble lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452846" lims:id="452846" salutation="no"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452847" lims:id="452847" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="yes" list-item="no"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452848" lims:id="452848">Préambule</MarginalNote><Text>Attendu :</Text></Provision><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452849" lims:id="452849" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="no" list-item="no"><Text>que c’est le 9 avril 1917, sur la crête de Vimy, que les Canadiens de tous les coins du pays ont, pour la première fois, combattu côte à côte contre un ennemi commun;</Text></Provision><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452850" lims:id="452850" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="no" list-item="no"><Text>que d’aucuns estiment que ce combat constitue un point tournant pour le Canada et marque le début de son accession au statut de nation,</Text></Provision></Preamble><Enacts lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452851" lims:id="452851"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452852" lims:id="452852" language-align="yes" list-item="no" format-ref="indent-0-0"><Text>Sa Majesté, sur l’avis et avec le consentement du Sénat et de la Chambre des communes du Canada, édicte :</Text></Provision></Enacts></Introduction><Body lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452853" lims:id="452853"><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452854" lims:id="452854" level="1"><TitleText>Titre abrégé</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:lastAmendedDate="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452855" lims:id="452855"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452856" lims:id="452856">Titre abrégé</MarginalNote><Label>1</Label><Text><XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="V-1.8">Loi sur le Jour de la bataille de Vimy</XRefExternal>.</Text></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452857" lims:id="452857" level="1"><TitleText>Jour de la bataille de Vimy</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:lastAmendedDate="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452858" lims:id="452858"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452859" lims:id="452859">Jour de la bataille de Vimy</MarginalNote><Label>2</Label><Text>Le 9 avril est, dans tout le Canada, désigné comme « Jour de la bataille de Vimy ».</Text></Section><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:lastAmendedDate="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452860" lims:id="452860"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452861" lims:id="452861">Drapeau canadien en berne</MarginalNote><Label>3</Label><Text>Le 9 avril de chaque année, le drapeau du Canada est mis en berne sur la tour de la Paix.</Text></Section><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:lastAmendedDate="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452862" lims:id="452862"><MarginalNote lims:inforce-start-date="2003-04-03" lims:fid="452863" lims:id="452863">Statut</MarginalNote><Label>4</Label><Text>Il est entendu que le Jour de la bataille de Vimy n’est pas une fête légale ni un jour non juridique.</Text></Section></Body></Statute>